  "texts": [
    "We specifically use the 'chat' variant via Huggingfacefoot_7.• Llama 2 13B: This is the 13 billion parameter version of Llama 2 model [18].",
    "Similar to the previous one, we use the 'chat' variant from Huggingfacefoot_8.",
    "• Llama 3 8B: This is the 8 billion parameter variant of the more recent Llama 3 model [19].",
    "We use the 'instruct' variant of the model from Huggingfacefoot_9,since it is known to be well-suited for following instructions in the prompt.",
    "Due to resource constraints, we were unable to use larger variants of Llama 2 and Llama 3 models."
  ]
